Paperclip
Stores images in the file system rather than the database.


Either a gem or a plugin.

	To use the plugin: script/plugin install git://github.com/thoughtbot/paperclip.git
	Then generate (plugin or gem): script/generate paperclip product photo
	                                                         <model> <attribute>
	Then run the migrations.
	Change the model to include: has_attached_file :photo
	

